<br>
what i did was count swings with no haste over 3 minutes, then count haste over 3 minutes with all the haste buff, and came out with 131% more swings *aka 131% haste*<br>
<br>
this leads me to belive without a doubt the belt fits in the same slot as war cry of the vah shir (CODE wise), and thus lets you break the 100% haste cap. also have logged fights with soul binder witha rev whip proving you can have faster then 10 dly weapon.<br>
<br>
So, just wanted to say grats to my idol Acolytis for proving Rangers are useful as melee, and cheers to you guys and hope this info is useful!<br>
<br>
cheers! and keep on keepin on!<br>
